<h4 style="text-align: center;"></h4>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Desert Marigold School is a learning community where everyone grows. Guided by the <a href="https://desertmarigold.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Core-Principles-poster-13x19.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Core Principles </a>of Public Waldorf education, we seek excellence in every aspect of our work. Our developmentally sound, experiential approach brings educational experiences and content in an age-appropriate manner from pre-school through high school. Located on a beautiful, 12-acre campus at the foot of South Mountain, our biodynamic garden, protected nature pond, and resident farm animals give substance to our commitment to sustainability as an intrinsic part of our curriculum.</p>
<h4 style="text-align: center;"><em>…Bringing Creative Potential To Life   </em></h4>
